<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Error 404 | Motokass</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --color-primary: #1F3F7A;
      --color-primary-dark: #142C57;
      --color-primary-light: #2E5AA6;

      --color-white: #FFFFFF;
      --color-gray-light: #F4F6FA;
      --color-gray-medium: #D6DCE5;
      --color-gray-dark: #1A1A1A;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        var(--color-primary-dark),
        var(--color-primary)
      );
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--color-white);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Fondo decorativo técnico */
    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      background: var(--color-primary-light);
      opacity: 0.08;
      border-radius: 50%;
      top: -200px;
      right: -200px;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 40px;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .error-code {
      font-size: 150px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 80px;
      height: 4px;
      background-color: var(--color-white);
      margin: 20px auto 30px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--color-gray-light);
      margin-bottom: 35px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      background-color: var(--color-white);
      color: var(--color-primary-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--color-gray-medium);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--color-gray-light);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .error-code {
        font-size: 100px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="error-code">404</div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <h1>Página no encontrada</h1>
    <p>
      La ruta que intentas acceder no existe o ha sido movida.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Volver al inicio</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    © {new Date().getFullYear()} Motokass. Todos los derechos reservados.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
